Qiyan

551
00:28:49,100 --> 00:28:51,420
is just a coward of discredit.

552
00:28:51,620 --> 00:28:53,180
Everyone in the Silver City knows it.

553
00:28:53,180 --> 00:28:55,700
The silkworm business is
under the government’s strict control

554
00:28:55,980 --> 00:28:57,380
and the price is not high.

555
00:28:57,690 --> 00:28:58,520
Now,

556
00:28:59,020 --> 00:29:00,740
I didn’t expect anyone to secretly sell

557
00:29:01,060 --> 00:29:02,380
silkworm eggs overseas and create

558
00:29:02,380 --> 00:29:03,500
a black market,

559
00:29:03,940 --> 00:29:06,260
resulting in that the silkworm farmers
can’t even make a living.

560
00:29:06,620 --> 00:29:08,660
It is a fraud against all our neighbors.

561
00:29:08,780 --> 00:29:10,700
I can’t tolerate it.

562
00:29:10,940 --> 00:29:11,660
I agree on

563
00:29:11,980 --> 00:29:13,780
all you said.

564
00:29:13,940 --> 00:29:15,060
Moreover,

565
00:29:15,340 --> 00:29:16,060
you constructed private houses,

566
00:29:16,180 --> 00:29:18,060
ran casinos and tobacco houses,

567
00:29:18,140 --> 00:29:20,050
and did all the appealing things.

568
00:29:20,120 --> 00:29:21,340
Appalling things.

569
00:29:22,220 --> 00:29:22,780
Coward?

570
00:29:23,220 --> 00:29:23,620
Yes!

571
00:29:24,020 --> 00:29:25,340
You are just a coward!

572
00:29:25,500 --> 00:29:27,700
You flatter and play servant
to the government.

573
00:29:27,700 --> 00:29:29,940
I can never torture this gamble.

574
00:29:31,100 --> 00:29:32,650
Tolerate this gamble.

575
00:29:34,180 --> 00:29:34,780
Have I put it right?

576
00:29:35,060 --> 00:29:35,580
Almost.

577
00:29:35,660 --> 00:29:36,700
That is okay.

578
00:29:36,870 --> 00:29:38,220
What a despicable couple you are!

579
00:29:38,820 --> 00:29:39,940
Two against one, right?

580
00:29:40,360 --> 00:29:41,320
Let me tell you,

581
00:29:41,460 --> 00:29:42,940
I am never afraid of anything!

582
00:29:43,780 --> 00:29:44,660
Come on.

583
00:29:45,180 --> 00:29:47,500
They showed no respect to me.

584
00:29:47,780 --> 00:29:48,220
Give it to me.

585
00:29:49,480 --> 00:29:50,200
Listen,

586
00:29:50,420 --> 00:29:51,540
give it to me

587
00:29:51,820 --> 00:29:53,680
or our silkworm business will be busted.

588
00:29:55,380 --> 00:29:56,260
Hurry.

589
00:29:59,180 --> 00:30:00,100
Give it to me.

590
00:30:02,700 --> 00:30:04,330
I use it as a chip against you.

591
00:30:04,340 --> 00:30:05,580
= Silk Token =

592
00:30:07,220 --> 00:30:08,940
It finally appeared.

593
00:30:08,940 --> 00:30:11,500
This token is equivalent
to three years’ silk tax.

594
00:30:11,660 --> 00:30:12,860
Only three families have it in the city.

595
00:30:13,380 --> 00:30:14,460
It has the same value

596
00:30:14,460 --> 00:30:15,300
as your chip.

597
00:30:15,660 --> 00:30:16,380
Get started.

598
00:30:16,940 --> 00:30:18,860
But throwing dices

599
00:30:19,420 --> 00:30:19,980
isn’t exciting enough.

600
00:30:20,500 --> 00:30:21,980
Let’s do something new.

601
00:30:22,420 --> 00:30:23,580
Good.

602
00:30:24,820 --> 00:30:26,900
I agree.

603
00:30:27,140 --> 00:30:28,940
Why does Master Long
have to change the way of gambling now?

604
00:30:29,220 --> 00:30:36,870
Master Long!

605
00:30:37,110 --> 00:30:38,340
Hey, man!

606
00:30:39,340 --> 00:30:41,380
Could you tell me their identities?

607
00:30:41,510 --> 00:30:42,620
You mustn’t be a native.

608
00:30:42,750 --> 00:30:44,460
This is the master of Longzhu Gang.

609
00:30:44,460 --> 00:30:47,710
Master Long! Master Long! Master Long!

610
00:30:47,720 --> 00:30:49,460
Boy, come here.

611
00:30:51,870 --> 00:30:54,350
May I exchange this silver ingot
with your bowl?

612
00:30:57,180 --> 00:30:57,820
Promise me.

613
00:30:58,060 --> 00:30:59,780
Use this silver ingot to buy

614
00:30:59,900 --> 00:31:02,060
a piece of new clothes
for each of your brothers

615
00:31:02,140 --> 00:31:02,900
and have a haircut.

616
00:31:03,180 --> 00:31:05,340
It is the Dragon Headraising Day today.

617
00:31:05,540 --> 00:31:06,500
As the dragon raises its head,
you should too.

618
00:31:07,300 --> 00:31:08,060
Thank you, sister.

619
00:31:08,060 --> 00:31:08,520
You are welcome.

620
00:31:11,300 --> 00:31:11,860
Qiyan,

621
00:31:12,460 --> 00:31:13,260
do you remember this?

622
00:31:14,940 --> 00:31:17,260
Let’s use this bowl for a gamble today.

623
00:31:19,820 --> 00:31:21,620
What gamble can it be

624
00:31:22,380 --> 00:31:23,420
with the broken bowl of a beggar?

625
00:31:24,060 --> 00:31:25,740
Wrap it up in a piece of cloth
and smash it.

626
00:31:26,020 --> 00:31:27,220
Count the fragments
and guess if it is an odd or even number.

627
00:31:27,460 --> 00:31:28,060
Okay?

628
00:31:31,780 --> 00:31:32,300
Well…

629
00:31:32,980 --> 00:31:34,580
You were really heroic just now.

630
00:31:35,540 --> 00:31:37,740
There is still time for you
to admit defeat.

631
00:31:42,780 --> 00:31:43,900
If you win,

632
00:31:43,900 --> 00:31:46,420
you will be sole owner
of the lower classes in the Silver City.

633
00:31:46,420 --> 00:31:47,460
Will you bet on it?

634
00:31:47,460 --> 00:31:47,860
Yes.

635
00:31:49,260 --> 00:31:49,940
I will.

636
00:32:04,500 --> 00:32:06,740
Start.

637
00:32:11,060 --> 00:32:11,660
Even.

638
00:32:12,540 --> 00:32:13,500
I guess it is even.

639
00:32:14,660 --> 00:32:15,220
No.

640
00:32:15,820 --> 00:32:17,380
We must take turns.

641
00:32:17,460 --> 00:32:19,020
If I also bet on an even number,

642
00:32:19,260 --> 00:32:21,260
the gamble will just be invalid
regardless of the result.

643
00:32:21,660 --> 00:32:23,380
Whoever starts will be the first.

644
00:32:23,420 --> 00:32:24,820
Don’t take me as a fool.

645
00:32:26,140 --> 00:32:26,620
Fine.

646
00:32:27,140 --> 00:32:28,660
It is at your convenience this time.

647
00:32:29,180 --> 00:32:29,860
I bet on an odd number.

648
00:32:44,340 --> 00:32:44,660
One.

649
00:32:45,140 --> 00:32:45,460
Two.

650
00:32:46,700 --> 00:32:47,020
Three.

651
00:32:48,020 --> 00:32:48,540
Four.

652
00:32:49,820 --> 00:32:50,340
Five.

653
00:32:51,180 --> 00:32:51,580
Six.

654
00:32:52,940 --> 00:32:53,340
Seven.

655
00:32:54,700 --> 00:32:55,100
Eight.

656
00:32:55,940 --> 00:32:56,340
Nine.

657
00:32:57,140 --> 00:32:58,360
We won! We won! We won!

658
00:32:58,360 --> 00:32:59,000
Nine fragments!

659
00:32:59,020 --> 00:32:59,690
Wonderful!

660
00:32:59,700 --> 00:33:01,290
We won!

661
00:33:01,300 --> 00:33:02,020
- Wait!
- We won…

662
00:33:03,700 --> 00:33:04,980
I must count it personally.

663
00:33:08,060 --> 00:33:09,860
Interesting, very interesting.

664
00:33:10,380 --> 00:33:12,700
Wu Lin, go and check Master Long.

665
00:33:13,580 --> 00:33:15,380
Also that person. Check them both.

666
00:33:16,170 --> 00:33:16,700
Yes.

667
00:33:19,660 --> 00:33:20,100
Master.

668
00:33:22,460 --> 00:33:24,780
We won. We won. We won.

669
00:33:26,060 --> 00:33:34,040
- Master Long!
- We won! Master! Master Long!

670
00:33:37,580 --> 00:33:40,340
Even a child knows
not to forget the origin.

671
00:33:40,780 --> 00:33:42,540
You called it a broken bowl
at first sight.

672
00:33:42,540 --> 00:33:44,980
I know you have forgotten your origin.

673
00:33:45,260 --> 00:33:46,900
In the drought over ten years ago,

674
00:33:46,900 --> 00:33:49,260
every family in the Silver City
had a lotus bowl like this for begging.

675
00:33:49,540 --> 00:33:51,420
Haven’t you used this bowl for begging?

676
00:33:52,380 --> 00:33:54,100
Look at it carefully with your eyes.

677
00:33:54,340 --> 00:33:56,060
All lotus bowls have

678
00:33:56,100 --> 00:33:58,140
a lotus shape with nine petals.

679
00:34:03,060 --> 00:34:04,300
A bowl with nine petals

680
00:34:04,300 --> 00:34:05,220
will most probably

681
00:34:05,220 --> 00:34:07,380
be broken into fragments of an odd number.

682
00:34:10,860 --> 00:34:12,220
- The master has won!
- Great!

683
00:34:12,220 --> 00:34:20,020
- Master Long!
- Master Long has won!

684
00:34:20,020 --> 00:34:21,300
Come on, bros,

685
00:34:21,380 --> 00:34:22,230
= Silk Token =
We must

686
00:34:22,230 --> 00:34:23,530
have a good drink today.

687
00:34:23,540 --> 00:34:24,220
All right!

688
00:34:24,220 --> 00:34:25,260
We won! We won!

689
00:34:27,100 --> 00:34:27,980
= Title Deed =

690
00:34:29,620 --> 00:34:30,700
= Commercial Title Deed =

691
00:34:37,900 --> 00:34:39,060
Master, look at these!

692
00:34:42,060 --> 00:34:44,100
How could you use these as title deeds!

693
00:34:44,780 --> 00:34:45,980
You lost this game!

694
00:34:45,980 --> 00:34:46,820
What?

695
00:34:48,260 --> 00:34:49,100
Well, these are…

696
00:34:49,700 --> 00:34:51,260
How dare you conspire

697
00:34:51,500 --> 00:34:53,860
with a swindler to cheat me!

698
00:34:55,020 --> 00:34:56,220
Listen, my bros of the Snake Gang,

699
00:34:56,620 --> 00:34:57,300
let’s get to the fighting!

700
00:34:57,420 --> 00:34:58,060
Go get them.

701
00:34:58,340 --> 00:34:58,780
Xiaoqin!

702
00:34:58,780 --> 00:34:59,900
Be careful, Your Highness!

703
00:34:59,900 --> 00:35:01,020
Catch that dude!

704
00:35:01,020 --> 00:35:01,780
Let’s go, Your Highness!

705
00:35:01,910 --> 00:35:02,540
- Let’s go!
- Don’t run away!

706
00:35:09,220 --> 00:35:10,860
Stop, you profiteer!

707
00:35:12,500 --> 00:35:13,380
There is no escape for you.

708
00:35:15,020 --> 00:35:15,900
Stop there!

709
00:35:17,500 --> 00:35:18,820
How dare you take away my properties!

710
00:35:18,820 --> 00:35:19,820
Return the silver ingots
and silkworm eggs.

711
00:35:19,820 --> 00:35:20,420
Let go.

712
00:35:21,960 --> 00:35:22,900
Give them back to me.

713
00:35:39,540 --> 00:35:41,900
I didn’t expect the rich guy of Xinsilu

714
00:35:41,900 --> 00:35:43,180
would steal such little money

715
00:35:43,380 --> 00:35:44,940
in such a despicable way.

716
00:35:45,060 --> 00:35:46,180
Shame on you!

717
00:35:46,540 --> 00:35:47,660
I just want one single article.

718
00:35:47,980 --> 00:35:49,260
Nothing for you.

719
00:35:56,860 --> 00:35:57,700
You owe me this time.

720
00:36:01,260 --> 00:36:01,900
It is a draw now.

721
00:36:06,820 --> 00:36:07,900
Let go. Let go.

722
00:36:07,900 --> 00:36:08,780
You let go.

723
00:36:22,660 --> 00:36:23,660
= Liquor =

724
00:36:28,300 --> 00:36:30,060
I heard a sound here just now.

725
00:36:34,420 --> 00:36:34,860
Go and search.

726
00:36:34,860 --> 00:36:35,540
Follow me.

727
00:36:53,940 --> 00:36:54,740
Master.

728
00:37:31,900 --> 00:37:33,180
