729
00:37:33,340 --> 00:37:34,460
What a pity!

730
00:37:37,580 --> 00:37:38,260
Mater Qi.

731
00:37:38,420 --> 00:37:39,140
Please,

732
00:37:39,300 --> 00:37:41,500
it is my private cellar under here.

733
00:37:41,820 --> 00:37:43,460
Nobody knows it. There is nobody in it.

734
00:37:43,820 --> 00:37:44,490
Listen,

735
00:37:44,900 --> 00:37:46,980
I will send you some jars of liquor later.

736
00:37:49,500 --> 00:37:51,380
Let’s go. I will be waiting for you.

737
00:37:51,410 --> 00:37:52,500
- Okay.
- Let’s go.

738
00:37:53,210 --> 00:37:54,190
Mind your steps, Master Qi.

