But I saw officials of the Silver City

756
00:39:02,780 --> 00:39:04,380
gambling publicly with tokens

757
00:39:04,380 --> 00:39:06,100
at Wanhua today.

758
00:39:06,300 --> 00:39:07,620
It is really out of expectation.

759
00:39:09,260 --> 00:39:09,860
Your Highness!

760
00:39:10,740 --> 00:39:12,780
