762
00:39:16,580 --> 00:39:17,460
Never mind.

763
00:39:18,420 --> 00:39:20,180
I am tired today.

764
00:39:20,540 --> 00:39:22,900
I have asked my daughter to arrange
for your accommodation.

765
00:39:23,460 --> 00:39:24,780
She is a careful and good-tempered girl.

766
00:39:25,060 --> 00:39:26,420
Please ask for her assistance

767
