I won this game against Qiyan.

774
00:39:52,220 --> 00:39:53,700
The chips are certainly mine.

775
00:39:54,140 --> 00:39:55,740
You wouldn’t have won it without me.

776
00:39:56,700 --> 00:39:57,340
Yes,

777
00:39:57,740 --> 00:39:59,780
