Frankly,

780
00:40:11,060 --> 00:40:12,900
I may look so honored

781
00:40:12,900 --> 00:40:13,980
as the gang master outside.

782
00:40:14,620 --> 00:40:16,660
But I have many brothers and sisters

783
00:40:16,660 --> 00:40:17,500
to feed back home.

784
00:40:19,780 --> 00:40:22,380
I have been making daily breads
since my childhood.

785
00:40:23,580 --> 00:40:25,380
I get up early

786
00:40:25,820 --> 00:40:26,940
and go to bed late.

787
00:40:28,100 --> 00:40:29,780
I am always hungry.

788
00:40:30,580 --> 00:40:31,580
I also have to sell bean curd.

789
00:40:32,460 --> 00:40:34,540
I have no parents.

790
00:40:35,100 --> 00:40:36,100
